text: Tone Dečman (26 June 1913 - 1989) was a Slovenian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1913 births Category:1989 deaths Category:Slovenian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Yugoslavia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ljubljana
